[[Playhouse Disney]] |terr serv 1= |terr chan 1= |sat serv 1= [[SKY]] |sat chan 1= Channel 614 |web= http://www.toondisney.it }} ''Toon Disney Italy'' was a TV channel which broadcasted cartoons from [[Italy]] and other countries. It was launched in 2004. Toon Disney Italy was the last [[Toon Disney]] available worldwide, since the rest were replaced by [[Disney Cinemagic]] in some countries and [[Disney XD]] in most countries. [[Jetix (Italy)|Jetix]] was already replaced by the Italian version of [[Disney XD (Italy)|Disney XD]]. After its launch in 2004, [[Toon Disney]] launched a time shift channel: Toon Disney +1.
